reviewText: Well, I know have this twice, "Band From Hell" is the same as "Neowolf" be careful. Exact same movies with different covers. This is a very silly movies and pretty low budget but it had some things in it that kept me interested. don't expect too much and just kind of have a good time. Veronica Cartwright as a werewolf hunter, haha.

Not only was the movie subpar...but I had already bought this under another title "Neowolf"

That kinda sucked lol

Mixing vampires with rockers yet to be new idea - Wild Zero, for instance. Neither sexing the vampire shows- Twilight (Two-Disc Special Edition) is the latest hit of. What makes this movie different is a mix of scarcity for both music and sex and abundance of sex delusions with no reason yet for a handsome youngster in expensive car while begging potential, old-looking college girlfriend for favours.
